creator: Wiv
descriptionHtml:
With a photo designer filter, you can enhance your photos by changing the color of your eye lens, or by putting blush onto your cheeks, with lots of skin tone foundation effect choosing the right foundation for your pictures. A photo blur option is also available. You can brush blurriness on any part of your picture also can set its intensity, and if you don't like the blur effect on your photo you can erase it.

With colorful lips, you can create cool looks, also you can add whiteness to your photos or to your teeth to enhance your smile. All these features made it easy for you to create simple yet classy photos.

Photo Designer Filter

Main Features

- Photo whitening with brush and erase tool.
- Face foundation with photo preview option.
- Editor for eyes.
- Put blush on.
- Blur photo by brushing the effect on it.

Photo whitening with brush and erase tool You can retouch your photos with the whitening option, this filter make your photo clear. You can also add whiteness to your teeth to get a perfect smile. You can add whiteness to your whole photo including background or just brush whiteness on your selfie face. With erase option easily erase the effect from your photo if you don't like it.

Lip Color changer with photo preview option Turn your no-makeup selfies into something attractive by adding different shades of colors on your lips. Up to 30+ shades make your lips more beautiful. Add shade to your lips or make them funky by adding bold lip colors.

Editor for eyes With different color options change your eye lens color, give your eyes a spark by adding different shades to it. You can enhance your eyes by enlarging them, also with an adjustment bar, you can set the size according to your face. Brighten your eye to brighten your selfies all with this editor. Preview easily your non-edited photo to make a comparison on both.

Also, you can minimize the under-eye circle by adjusting its intensity on your eyes. Make your selfies or photo look fresh by editing it and hiding dark circle beneath eyes.

Put blush on Ad blush on on your cheeks and get freshness on your selfies easily. With blush palette choose your own color to add on your cheeks, make peachy cheeks or bronze look all with this cheek editor. You can preview at any time if you don't like your cheek makeup. This photo designer filter make can make your photos enhanced by editing them with photo editor.

Blur photo by brushing the effect on it- Blur all the perfection fro your photos or selfies, you can also only blur the picture background too. With blur effect blur half of your photo or blur on the whole by brushing it. You can easily erase the effect from the photo whenever you want to, you can erase the blur effect if you think it is not necessary to add in a specific area or your picture quality get affected.
descriptionShort: With Photo Designer Filter customize your photos easily.
